Dear Friend,
I am Barrister Jacob Morgan, a solicitor at law. I have an important
message for you concerning the death of late Engr. Anton B., Who works
with SHELL DEVELOPMENT COMPANY HERE. He is a national of your country,
who bears the same last name as you, and his fund valued at
US$10.5million dollars was left behind in one of the banks here in my
country (Togo) as a result of a car accident that took his life. If
your last name is actually (This) kindly contact me as soon as you get
this message to let my intention known to you.

Thanks.
Best Regards
Mr. Jacob Morgan
Private Email-jacobmorganesqtg@gmail.com
